metadata.name: "Wild Thing" Howler Dawes
metadata.description:
"Wild Thing, You make my heart sing!"

On the Sunshine Coast of Australia, you wrestle crocs and you swim with sharks. You learn to go wild.  Then there's “Wild Thing” Howler Dawes.  A rocker by night, surf instructor by day, and the truth or dare champion of Australia. Here's a guy who thinks playing peek-a-boo with an angry crocodile(check the scar) is a lazy Sunday afternoon.
